com.perfectomobile.test

Class BasicTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.perfectomobile.test.BasicTest
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CommunitySearchPost, CommunitySignIn, CommunitySignIn_IOS, EmptyTest, KeywordDrivenTest

    public abstract class BasicTest
extends java.lang.Object
    BasicTest is the abstract base class for all tests which are implemented with the Beton framework. The BasicTest class is responsible for:
    • Reading the capabilities file and instantiate drivers per capabilities sets
    • Dispatching the tests

    BasicTest provides methods for the following:

    • Storing/Reading system properties
    • Reading device properties
    • Writing test results to DB (currently Excel only)
    • Writing test results to HTML report
    Author:
    Avner Gershtansky
